      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i just noticed some of the newer textbooks and legal critiques mention that some people think this doctrine is actually dangerous because it lets judges make up rights that aren't in the text. how should i explain those criticisms to my students so they understand why some people oppose it?",
      "source": "evaluator"
